      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error (distinct from discretization error) is scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 credibility factor applicability table. The solver has been verified via manufactured solutions (Numerical code verification factor), and residual convergence to 1e-6 is documented for all runs. Separate solver error quantification is not required at this risk level."
