      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. The simulation workflow is executed by a single trained analyst following a documented simulation protocol (SOP-CFD-CBP-003). Independent review of boundary condition setup and post-processing scripts was performed but a formal use error study is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/mf-001",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty quantification is scoped out at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model is the community standard for rotating blood pump CFD (per FDA 2017 computational fluid dynamics guidance). The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) is the accepted regulatory standard. Alternative model form comparison is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
