      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA benchmark dataset (Hariharan et al. 2011) used for validation was collected with five pump units manufactured to the same specification. Unit-to-unit geometric variation was characterized at ±0.05 mm on critical dimensions, which is within the simulation geometry tolerance band. Formal sample adequacy analysis is not required at this risk level."
